@{b}INSTALLATION@{ub}

MagicTV requires the AGA chipset.

  *  Remove any old version of MagicTV from WBStartup or C:

  *  Copy MagicTV to C:

  *  Put the line:
      @{b}MagicTV@{ub}
     in your Startup-Sequence, directly after SetPatch.



